7. Trust and Safety Design

7.1 Evidence-first rendering

No summary without source linkage.

7.2 Inference labeling

Mark statements as:
	•	Confirmed
	•	Probable
	•	Contested
	•	Speculative

7.3 Propaganda detection

Hound layer flags:
	•	excessive emotional loading
	•	unsupported causal jumps
	•	omission patterns
	•	quote laundering
	•	source monoculture
	•	bot-like repetition

7.4 Adversarial cross-pass

Each event should be run through:
	•	one extraction pass
	•	one verification pass
	•	one adversarial pass

7.5 No hidden profile defaults

Every default profile must be visible to the user.

