8. User Experience Requirements

Event page should include
	•	headline
	•	canonical fact table
	•	source list
	•	uncertainty list
	•	frame comparison
	•	raw-source expansion option

User should be able to
	•	choose a profile
	•	compare profiles side by side
	•	create a custom profile
	•	inspect source provenance
	•	see confidence and contradiction markers

User should never be forced into
	•	one hidden narrative
	•	one default ideology disguised as neutrality

