9. Recommended MVP

Start small.

MVP scope

Choose one domain:
	•	finance
	•	geopolitics
	•	public policy
	•	science news

MVP pipeline
	1.	Pull 5 to 10 sources on one event
	2.	Extract claims
	3.	Merge into fact graph
	4.	Define 3 bias profiles
	5.	Generate 3 summaries
	6.	Render comparison table

MVP success criteria
	•	Same facts, different explicit frames
	•	User can see why summaries differ
	•	Contradictions are visible
	•	Source links are intact

