11. Key Algorithms

Claim clustering

Group semantically equivalent claims.

Contradiction detection

Find claims that cannot all be true at once.

Source diversity scoring

Penalize monoculture.

Evidence density scoring

Reward claims backed by multiple independent sources.

Frame weighting engine

Re-rank salience without changing underlying evidence.

Narrative delta engine

Measure how outputs differ across profiles.

